00:35:55.830 --> 00:35:57.520 align:middle line:90%
You go into some depth of that.

00:35:57.520 --> 00:35:59.620 align:middle line:90%
And let's talk about that.

00:35:59.620 --> 00:36:01.760 align:middle line:84%
I mean, just like
women flying on brooms

00:36:01.760 --> 00:36:03.900 align:middle line:84%
