00:36:11.555 --> 00:36:12.769 align:middle line:90%
and so forth.

00:36:12.769 --> 00:36:13.810 align:middle line:90%
So let's talk about that.

00:36:13.810 --> 00:36:15.393 align:middle line:84%
>>HATSIS: Well, it's
