00:37:35.820 --> 00:37:39.220 align:middle line:84%
It was just a form of-- before
the internet, TV, radio,

00:37:39.220 --> 00:37:40.890 align:middle line:90%
it was just something to do.

00:37:40.890 --> 00:37:44.560 align:middle line:84%
There was another case I
