00:38:05.770 --> 00:38:08.670 align:middle line:84%
But it seems like they were
just out there doing this.

00:38:08.670 --> 00:38:10.170 align:middle line:84%
They were in a
strawberry patch just

00:38:10.170 --> 00:38:13.860 align:middle line:84%
trying to entertain themselves
in some form or another.

00:38:13.860 --> 00:38:16.180 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Like people do
