the Medicine Woman.

00:38:52.090 --> 00:38:55.230 align:middle line:84%
And my child ends
up dying anyway.

00:38:55.230 --> 00:38:56.930 align:middle line:84%
And now it's like,
oh, damn, I need

00:38:56.930 --> 00:38:59.060 align:middle line:84%
I need some kind of
satisfaction from this.

00:38:59.060 --> 00:39:02.960 align:middle line:84%
So now you're brought
into trial, right?

00:39:02.960 --> 00:39:05.430 align:middle line:84%
Or you're brought into
the secular courts.

00:39:05.430 --> 00:39:08.540 align:middle line:84%
And now we understand, of
course-- again, we "know"--

00:39:08.540 --> 00:39:09.940 align:middle line:90%
that there's not just one witch.

00:39:09.940 --> 00:39:11.970 align:middle line:90%
There's a society witches.

00:39:11.970 --> 00:39:15.096 align:middle line:84%
So then you're tortured
into confessing,

00:39:15.096 --> 00:39:17.900 align:middle line:84%
well, Suzanne outside
or something was also

00:39:17.900 --> 00:39:18.700 align:middle line:90%
part of this.

00:39:18.700 --> 00:39:19.790 align:middle line:90%
So then she's brought in.

00:39:19.790 --> 00:39:21.180 align:middle line:90%
Now, she's not a witch at all.

00:39:21.180 --> 00:39:22.555 align:middle line:84%
She's just somebody
that was name

00:39:22.555 --> 00:39:25.010 align:middle line:84%
dropped because, when those
thumbscrews are going in,

00:39:25.010 --> 00:39:26.218 align:middle line:90%
