00:39:26.218 --> 00:39:28.130 align:middle line:84%
It's like we know today
torture doesn't work.

00:39:28.130 --> 00:39:31.990 align:middle line:84%
So you have now Suzanne
is going to say,

00:39:31.990 --> 00:39:34.920 align:middle line:84%
oh, this other person,
Ellie or whatever, now she's

00:39:34.920 --> 00:39:36.500 align:middle line:90%
accused of witchcraft.

00:39:36.500 --> 00:39:39.807 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden, you
have this large-- all

00:39:39.807 --> 00:39:41.640 align:middle line:84%
these different people
are now being brought

00:39:41.640 --> 00:39:44.790 align:middle line:84%
in and under Inquisitorial
procedure and promises

00:39:44.790 --> 00:39:46.886 align:middle line:90%
of freedom if they confess.

00:39:46.886 --> 00:39:48.260 align:middle line:84%
They're all saying,
yeah, OK, I'm

00:39:48.260 --> 00:39:49.650 align:middle line:90%
a part of this large conspiracy.

00:39:49.650 --> 00:39:51.880 align:middle line:84%
And before they know it,
they end up at the stake.

00:39:51.880 --> 00:39:54.290 align:middle line:84%
But usually, most
of the cases started

00:39:54.290 --> 00:39:58.290 align:middle line:84%
with one woman being
brought to trial,

00:39:58.290 --> 00:39:59.790 align:middle line:90%
just like Matteuccia was.

00:39:59.790 --> 00:40:02.410 align:middle line:84%
She was brought initially
because her neighbors wanted

00:40:02.410 --> 00:40:03.210 align:middle line:90%
to.

00:40:03.210 --> 00:40:06.030 align:middle line:84%
But it was also weird with
her, because it's a mix.

00:40:06.030 --> 00:40:09.370 align:middle line:84%
Because she was only brought
to trial to the secular courts

00:40:09.370 --> 00:40:11.020 align:middle line:84%
because this guy
Bernardino of Sienna

00:40:11.020 --> 00:40:13.145 align:middle line:84%
had convinced her neighbors
that what she was doing

00:40:13.145 --> 00:40:14.380 align:middle line:90%
was witchcraft.

00:40:14.380 --> 00:40:15.180 align:middle line:90%
So it's odd.

00:40:15.180 --> 00:40:16.055 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: It is odd.

00:40:16.055 --> 00:40:16.930 align:middle line:90%
I see.

00:40:16.930 --> 00:40:18.340 align:middle line:90%
Yes, I get what you're saying.

00:40:18.340 --> 00:40:21.480 align:middle line:84%
>>HATSIS: Yeah, it's everybody
not realizing it but acting

00:40:21.480 --> 00:40:23.550 align:middle line:90%
in unison to create this.

00:40:23.550 --> 00:40:26.050 align:middle line:84%
And in some cases-- there
