00:40:30.770 --> 00:40:32.175 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Jeez.

00:40:32.175 --> 00:40:34.800 align:middle line:84%
Let's speak about the Rhineland
since you talked about Germany.

00:40:34.800 --> 00:40:39.690 align:middle line:84%
I wanted to bring that up,
ergot, the fungus on the rye.

00:40:39.690 --> 00:40:40.490 align:middle line:90%
>>HATSIS: Yes.

00:40:40.490 --> 00:40:41.864 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Let's
talk about that.

00:40:41.864 --> 00:40:44.590 align:middle line:84%
>>HATSIS: Yeah, ergot was
used for different reasons,

00:40:44.590 --> 00:40:48.170 align:middle line:84%
mostly to help stimulate
contractions and birth control.

00:40:48.170 --> 00:40:51.120 align:middle line:84%
And that's actually a
perfect example of something.

00:40:51.120 --> 00:40:56.560 align:middle line:84%
So a woman giving birth is
given ergot to stimulate

00:40:56.560 --> 00:40:58.310 align:middle line:90%
the contractions to help along.

00:40:58.310 --> 00:40:59.910 align:middle line:84%
Now she starts
having what we would

00:40:59.910 --> 00:41:02.120 align:middle line:90%
call a psychedelic experience.

00:41:02.120 --> 00:41:03.360 align:middle line:90%
Now she's in a lot of pain.

00:41:03.360 --> 00:41:04.210 align:middle line:90%
She's giving birth.

00:41:04.210 --> 00:41:06.190 align:middle line:84%
That's going to
affect her mindset.

00:41:06.190 --> 00:41:07.890 align:middle line:84%
And now all of a
sudden, she's going

00:41:07.890 --> 00:41:10.100 align:middle line:84%
to think that there was
a spell cast on her.

00:41:10.100 --> 00:41:13.690 align:middle line:84%
Because of the state of
medicine at the time,

00:41:13.690 --> 00:41:16.210 align:middle line:84%
most children died
during childbirth.

00:41:16.210 --> 00:41:19.950 align:middle line:84%
So now you have a woman
who, unfortunately, doesn't

00:41:19.950 --> 00:41:23.110 align:middle line:84%
know any better,
but in her mind,

00:41:23.110 --> 00:41:27.140 align:middle line:84%
well, I went to this wise
woman, she cast a spell on me,

00:41:27.140 --> 00:41:29.690 align:middle line:84%
I had all these visions of
demons flying through the air,

00:41:29.690 --> 00:41:31.820 align:middle line:90%
and my child died.

00:41:31.820 --> 00:41:34.870 align:middle line:84%
And now that woman is now
accused of witchcraft.

00:41:34.870 --> 00:41:36.900 align:middle line:84%
She wasn't trying to
help deliver a child.

00:41:36.900 --> 00:41:39.670 align:middle line:84%
She wanted to kill
the child and perhaps

00:41:39.670 --> 00:41:41.634 align:middle line:90%
the mother, too, or something.

00:41:41.634 --> 00:41:43.550 align:middle line:84%
It's all really sad when
you read the records.

00:41:43.550 --> 00:41:44.950 align:middle line:10%
>> REGINA: And then you
had this inadvertent stuff,

00:41:44.950 --> 00:41:47.480 align:middle line:10%
like what was it called,
the Rhineland hysteria?

00:41:47.480 --> 00:41:50.300 align:middle line:90%
>>HATSIS: Oh, yeah.

00:41:50.300 --> 00:41:54.030 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes during a rainy season
and you get ergot onto crops.

00:41:54.030 --> 00:41:56.150 align:middle line:84%
And people might not
have realized it.

00:41:56.150 --> 00:41:58.820 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Attached to the rye,
a fungus that attached to rye

00:41:58.820 --> 00:41:59.300 align:middle line:90%
grain.

00:41:59.300 --> 00:42:01.383 align:middle line:84%
>>HATSIS: Yeah, exactly,
a fungus attached to rye.

