want, but--

00:42:34.470 --> 00:42:37.409 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: These are just
interesting glimpses of how

00:42:37.409 --> 00:42:39.450 align:middle line:84%
these things happen in
history, which, of course,

00:42:39.450 --> 00:42:40.710 align:middle line:90%
today would never occur.

