Well, there must be Satan.

00:42:49.000 --> 00:42:50.790 align:middle line:90%
But how could Satan be here?

00:42:50.790 --> 00:42:53.380 align:middle line:84%
Well, there must be
witches conjuring Satan.

00:42:53.380 --> 00:42:56.610 align:middle line:84%
And it was just like
this was the illogic.

00:42:56.610 --> 00:42:57.410 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:42:57.410 --> 00:43:01.619 align:middle line:84%
So let's talk about some
of the drugs themselves

00:43:01.619 --> 00:43:03.660 align:middle line:84%
that were used, some of
the herbs that were used.

00:43:03.660 --> 00:43:05.750 align:middle line:84%
Because a really popular
one in the day-- and we

00:43:05.750 --> 00:43:08.030 align:middle line:84%
can just talk about some
of the really practical

00:43:08.030 --> 00:43:09.970 align:middle line:90%
uses of it-- with opium.

00:43:09.970 --> 00:43:11.240 align:middle line:90%
Opium was big by itself.

00:43:11.240 --> 00:43:12.590 align:middle line:90%
I mean, even in child care.

00:43:12.590 --> 00:43:13.940 align:middle line:90%
>>HATSIS: Absolutely.

00:43:13.940 --> 00:43:18.700 align:middle line:84%
So one of the major problems
in the Inquisitorial records

00:43:18.700 --> 00:43:21.775 align:middle line:84%
is that they didn't
care what drug was used.

00:43:21.775 --> 00:43:25.180 align:middle line:84%
It was a secondary concern to
the fact that a drug was used.

00:43:25.180 --> 00:43:26.870 align:middle line:84%
So most of the time
you get that word

00:43:26.870 --> 00:43:30.610 align:middle line:84%
"vene," which just means
poison, or certes herbes,

00:43:30.610 --> 00:43:34.160 align:middle line:84%
which just means a certain kind
of herb, or pocula amatori,

00:43:34.160 --> 00:43:37.720 align:middle line:84%
and who knows what was in
that, the love filter, who

00:43:37.720 --> 00:43:38.930 align:middle line:90%
knows what was in that.

00:43:38.930 --> 00:43:43.580 align:middle line:84%
And it's only when you have
the physicians-- because most

00:43:43.580 --> 00:43:45.760 align:middle line:84%
of the time when a person
was brought into trial

00:43:45.760 --> 00:43:49.710 align:middle line:84%
or to be inquested, there was
a physician there also taking

00:43:49.710 --> 00:43:50.540 align:middle line:90%
notes.

00:43:50.540 --> 00:43:55.040 align:middle line:84%
And you have an inquisitor
saying, oh, it's the devil,

00:43:55.040 --> 00:43:55.840 align:middle line:90%
it's the devil.

00:43:55.840 --> 00:43:58.476 align:middle line:84%
And you have the
physician saying, nah,

00:43:58.476 --> 00:43:59.780 align:middle line:90%
she's probably on opium.

00:43:59.780 --> 00:44:00.770 align:middle line:90%
[BOTH LAUGHING]

00:44:00.770 --> 00:44:02.390 align:middle line:84%
Like that's probably
what that is.

00:44:02.390 --> 00:44:07.780 align:middle line:84%
And opium is a weird one,
because it didn't grow wildly

00:44:07.780 --> 00:44:09.020 align:middle line:90%
in these regions.

00:44:09.020 --> 00:44:11.040 align:middle line:84%
So people had access
to opium if they

00:44:11.040 --> 00:44:14.520 align:middle line:84%
were near a town that had an
apothecary that got opium.

00:44:14.520 --> 00:44:16.730 align:middle line:84%
But most of the
